Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.35,0:23:26.94,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be1.3\fad(250,250)}因为我们总是总是那么地开心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:29.82,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be1.3\fad(250,250)}难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:32.49,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be1.3\fad(250,250)}vivace 在五线谱上歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.90,0:23:39.49,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be1.3\fad(250,250)}vivace 响彻远方的春天
